#                                                                                                                                                                                                       

[media]

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

[media]

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

[media]

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

[media]

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

[media]

**Christmas Update**
- New Xmas Battlepass
- Christmas Ornament Hunt
- New Rudolf Bundle
- Christmas Themed Levels

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/499303746_2181339939044468_540727540857874572_n.mp4?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=TVispFJRt_gQ7kNvwEndE0t&_nc_oc=AdnMVhsGqJs11WK9MV7JLBeTHe96JIulbHweeoikMR4-RAsuIxzdo0NQVcNdKO4_-SY&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-2.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=hhX5W-Bk3FG2rpRp8eN5uw&oh=00_Aftm2uIXszEDQy1CKDhKplLSVX8rLTZW-bc3Bv-Lnaj39g&oe=69857A24)

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491821117_1430846481437060_8099142216261706884_n.mp4?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=cnfHl3UOTLEQ7kNvwGQ9ZWo&_nc_oc=AdnqGTCe55cKi_3ngZRjHROBg3_ENtpwqxCRH0dPQ_ynofqsFWnKgwGWeoRiuRMmde8&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=hhX5W-Bk3FG2rpRp8eN5uw&oh=00_Afuo8FLCIM2i9D2n8BsxQwqaKkRF8Z4pGB_a0nn83Di3NA&oe=69856F4C)
